OL,3,CSeveral banks experiencing app and
OL,4,Conline banking outages on payday
OL,6,FFirst Direct, Halifax, Nationwide,
OL,7,FLloyds Bank, TSB and Bank of Scotland
OL,8,Fhave reported online banking issues on
OL,9,FFriday morning, leaving many customers
OL,10,Funable to access their payday funds.
OL,12,FFor the second month in a row, major
OL,13,Fbanks have faced IT issues around
OL,14,Fpayday. Experts say online banking
OL,15,Fsystems often struggle with the surge
OL,16,Fin transactions as wages and bills are
OL,17,Fprocessed at the end of the month.
OL,19,FThe banks said they are working to fix
OL,20,Fthe issue and restore normal service.
