OL,6,FFirst Direct's website stated that
OL,7,Fboth its mobile and online banking
OL,8,Fwere "experiencing issues with
OL,9,Fpayments".
OL,11,FAccording to service status site
OL,12,FDownDetector, users reported issues
OL,13,Fwith several other banks, but none
OL,14,Fhave confirmed any problems so far.
OL,16,FFintech expert Chris Skinner said in
OL,17,Fthe wake of those outages that banks
OL,18,Fwere finding it "too hard to keep up"
OL,19,Fwith fast-moving technology.
